Title: Raptors swarm Embiid, but fall to 76ers
Description: TAMPA — All-Star center Joel Embiid didn’t get the ball much in the first half Tuesday night, but his Philadelphia teammates made the Raptors pay in a 109-102 victory. Tobias Harris scored 12 of his 23 points in the fourth quarter after the 76ers built a big early lead with long-range shooting,
Author: Tampa Bay Times
